{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 54,
  "title": "第五十四章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "善建者不拔，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善抱者不脫，"
    },
    {
      "text": "子孫以祭祀不輟。"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於身，其德乃真；修之於家，其德乃餘；"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於鄉，其德乃長；修之於國，其德乃豐；修之於天下，其德乃普。故以身觀身，以家觀家，以鄉觀鄉，以國觀國，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以天下觀天下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾何以知天下然哉？以此。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "固其根而後營其末，故不拔也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不貪於多，齊其所能，故不脫也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "子孫傳此道以祭祀則不輟也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以身及人也，修之身則真，修之家則有餘，修之不廢，所施轉大。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 52
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "彼皆然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以天下百姓心觀天下之道也，天下之道，逆順吉凶，亦皆如人之道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此上之所云也。言吾何以得知天下乎，察己以知之，不求於外也，所謂不出戶以知天下者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
